    <note>Mo(1) Junchen [1370] Great-grandsons, Ji [3678] and Zhang [3677], were respectively Sinong shaoqing in 1166-1167 and Zhedong tiju in 1196. Mo(1) Meng [1371] had the same generational name and address as his great grandsons. According to 1148 jinshi list, yijia #4 entry for his great grandson, Ji(2) [16372] (q.v.), Ji(2)'s great great granduncle established the household (weihu), which would be Junchen's uncle, who may have been the person who moved to Kaifeng. Zhejiang TZ, 123.27b; XCB, 505.17b; XZZTJ, 139.29b; SHY:ZG, 26.20a; 73.66a. CBD, 3, 2725.</note>
